data.description: Beautifully decorated and meticulously maintained Mt. Vernon model end unit townhome in prime location. This sun filled property with windows galore, located just minutes away from community club and Brenman Park. It features three bedrooms, two and half baths, one car garage and reserved parking space #203. The open main level floor plan seamlessly integrates a kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, adjoined by the family room featuring a cozy gas fireplace. TREX deck extends from the kitchen, providing a delightful outdoor space. The property has been freshly painted in a neutral color throughout, showcasing hardwood flooring on all stairs, main level, primary bedroom, and landing. HVAC system and furnace replaced in 2016. Custom blinds and plantation shutters adorn the windows throughout, adding to the home's overall elegance. A TEN!
